{"tid":871810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法允售軍備　台升級幻影戰機","createTime":"2018-10-22T08:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T09:10:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e02842a3dadcbcf7fcb67dc46d94b873d5c646e0","tid":871810,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181022/20527589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181022%2F20527589&d=ax1iBzcBQBHgfFlmKBArgBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a7f066d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181022%2F20527589&h=4e4647aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181022/20527589</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月22日 <br />\n<br />\n法允售軍備　台升級幻影戰機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181022/large/a1705a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181022%2Flarge%2Fa1705a.gif&h=aaadb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台軍幻影2000戰機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼美國向台灣售武，台灣國防部表示，已經與法國達梭公司（Dassault Aviation）簽訂為期5年、總值107億元新台幣（約27億港元）的飛機機身、零件合約，為台灣空軍的幻影2000戰機進行大修，並且提高戰機的高空攔截戰鬥力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擲27億　簽約5年<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，這次與法國廠商的合約，源自2016年空軍與法國軍備局簽訂5年一項後期的幻影2000戰機與雲母、魔法飛彈的整體後勤支援服務的協議。<br />\n<br />\n這次協議，法國軍備局將派相關技術服務團到台灣，檢整台灣的幻影2000戰機所需更換的後勤零附件，同時會為幻影戰機搭配的雲母、魔法導彈進行延長使用期及更新。報道指，該協議將會在今年正式啟動，完成後，空軍估計幻影2000戰機的妥善率，將由目前的60%提升至超過75%。<br />\n<br />\n台灣在1992年向法國採購60架幻影2000戰機，但由於法經常延遲提供相關零附件，造成台幻影戰機的妥善率一直無法提升，先後發生多宗意外，最少導致4名機師死亡。<br />\n<br />\n幻影2000為法國達梭公司公司製造之先進第四代戰鬥機，具有大型三角翼、無尾翼、單發動機構型等特點之多用途戰機，目前包括法國、台灣在內共有9個國家處於服役狀態。<br />\n<br />\n美國上月通過對台軍售，其中包括向台灣的F-16、F-5、IDF戰機及C130運輸機，提供航空系統備件及相關的支援系統，總值3.3億美元（約25.7億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《自由時報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n改革開放40年淪習造神騷"},{"pid":"7a372620369d3237612745bf8e0cabc4dac5f1a4","tid":871810,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"法國平時唔係唔賣比台灣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea004a8941c31588bfa1e7f05537308f6cef9ce","tid":871810,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a372620369d3237612745bf8e0cabc4dac5f1a4","tid":871810,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"法國平時唔係唔賣比台灣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"國際刑警單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d5416f63385d56f978b36d2236b9557359e96","tid":871810,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:07:54.000Z","msg":"買垃圾黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac9d8add276e8ea6864e225ceb27c62e2c01d79","tid":871810,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7d5416f63385d56f978b36d2236b9557359e96","tid":871810,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:07:54.000Z","msg":"買垃圾黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"重點唔係架機, <br />\n<br />\n係粒雲母飛彈"},{"pid":"d5848d3ebe8793f93610ade962f0e6c7b3f78299","tid":871810,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"台仔d法國武器火藥全部過期變質<br />\n<br />\n真係急到賴尿"},{"pid":"d9